Sentencas: Interconnected micropores play a critical role as fuel gas flow channels in solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC), which is quite difficult to prepare using conventional methods.
Titulo: Fabrication of particle-stacking porous anode for solid oxide fuel cell using laser powder bed fusion

Sentencas: In this work, an interconnected microporous structure of Ni-based anode was newly fabricated by laser powder bed fusion (LPBF), controlling the melting behavior of particles and stacking them up to form a high-porosity space net structure with point contacts.
Titulo: Fabrication of particle-stacking porous anode for solid oxide fuel cell using laser powder bed fusion

Sentencas: The results show that the YSZ sprayed powder initially behaves as nanoparticles, forming an unmanageable sub-microporous structure.
Titulo: Fabrication of particle-stacking porous anode for solid oxide fuel cell using laser powder bed fusion

Sentencas: After densification, however, it melts as microparticles and forms micropores distributing with a wider manageable range.
Titulo: Fabrication of particle-stacking porous anode for solid oxide fuel cell using laser powder bed fusion

Sentencas: In addition, densified YSZ powder forms interconnected pores with isolated islandshaped sintered particles finely distributed along the laser scanning direction at XY orientation.
Titulo: Fabrication of particle-stacking porous anode for solid oxide fuel cell using laser powder bed fusion

Sentencas: Due to a narrow molten pool and large sintering shrinkage generated, an overlapped area forms only at Z orientation.
Titulo: Fabrication of particle-stacking porous anode for solid oxide fuel cell using laser powder bed fusion

Sentencas: These overlaps can be improved by adding Ni element, behaving as a particle binder in the matrix, but this is easy to form Ni segregations and deteriorate the element homogeneity.
Titulo: Fabrication of particle-stacking porous anode for solid oxide fuel cell using laser powder bed fusion

Sentencas: In contrast, adding NiO can promote a finer composition distribution.
Titulo: Fabrication of particle-stacking porous anode for solid oxide fuel cell using laser powder bed fusion
